lead_paragraph: Zinedine Zidane's triumphant start as Real Madrid coach set the Bernabeu buzzing on Saturday and the 10-times European champions are hoping the 'Zizou effect' can return the world's richest club to winning ways.

headline.print_headline: 'Zizou Effect' at Real Has Bernabeu Buzzing
